OL,3,CMan faces murder charge 20 years after
OL,4,Cfatal shooting
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder 20
OL,7,Fyears after a fatal shooting in
OL,8,FSheffield.
OL,10,FIbrahim Ilyas was the victim of a
OL,11,Fdrive-by shooting in the Fir Vale area
OL,12,Fof the city on 3 June 2006.
OL,14,FThe 20-year-old had been sitting in a
OL,15,Fcar on Abbeyfield Road when he was
OL,16,Fkilled. Two other men in the car were
OL,17,Falso injured.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
