OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773155489
OL,3,CMan faces murder charge 20 years after
OL,4,Cfatal shooting
OL,6,FMohammed Ali, who was 24 at the time,
OL,7,Fwas jailed for a minimum of 30 years
OL,8,Fin 2007 for his murder, and two counts
OL,9,Fof attempted murder.
OL,11,FNow a second man, 44-year-old Faiser
OL,12,FHussain, been charged with Mr Ilyas's
OL,13,Fmurder, as well as two counts of
OL,14,Fattempted murder.
OL,16,FSouth Yorkshire Police said he was
OL,17,Farrested at Manchester Airport at the
OL,18,Fweekend.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
