OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773155489
OL,3,CMan faces murder charge 20 years after
OL,4,Cfatal shooting
OL,6,FHussain appeared before Sheffield
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Monday and was
OL,8,Fremanded into custody ahead of an
OL,9,Fappearance at Sheffield Crown Court on
OL,10,FTuesday.
OL,12,FThe victim's family had been informed,
OL,13,Fa police spokesperson said.
OL,15,FDet Ch Insp Tom Woodward said:
OL,16,F"Ibrahim was a young man whose life
OL,17,Fwas cut tragically short in the most
OL,18,Fdevastating of circumstances.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
